 python3-yaml,
Description: joystick UDP bridge and Betaflight MSP forwarder
 bt-joy reads joystick input, maps it to RC channel values, sends
 those values over UDP, and can forward them to Betaflight using MSP.
 The package installs client and server commands, YAML configuration
 examples, systemd service units, and manual pages.
